name: About Lines #2: Colouring
description:
After the sketches, the colouring. Fuelling imagination, making space for what comes next.

This piece is part of a series inspired by Japanese calligraphy and the works of German-French painter Hans Hartung (1904 - 1989).

Minted for #HEN500K · PNG, 4000 × 2500 px · Original artwork by Andreas Rau · Oslo, 2021
